8b6034c0338ab4c7d648f47983aad6da07e427e7dba47baabf85a1b3ddeeda47c8d7fbcd547a302c9a759b2943ee30d3e82c3b368d8582833a058e4671638a9e  90-android-touch-dev.rules"
